more difficult </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">in the absence of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">trust, and that trust can derive from demonstrations of expertise, perceived even-handedness, or </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">a sense of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">shared values.</span><a name="_ftnref47"></a><a href="#_ftn47">[47]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">A </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">serious </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">dilemma</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> arises now</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, recognised by many </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">independent</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">(i.e. University or Research Institute) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">climate </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">scientists</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">. I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">n seeking to put the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">c</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ience </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">and its</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> implications fo</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">r society </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">a